attributes.Long form description: The student is building a machine. They start by placing a lever, then sliding a shift into a mount peg. Next, they grab a screw and a nut and assemble them. Once the screw is in place, they grab a ratchet and tighten the screw into the peg. Then they shift the lever for every gear. After that, they grab a bench used for quality control and turn on a black box. Finally, they grab an orange remote and press a button on it twice.
